Name: color reference

Synonyms: color specifier, color reference, color descriptor

Type: glossary

Description:
Any valid way of describing a particular color that LiveCode can
understand. 

Colors can be referred to by color name, <HTML> -style specification, or
as three comma-separated numbers between zero and 255 (one for each of
red, blue, and green).

